cask install iterm2 2> /dev/null
cask install totalterminal 2> /dev/null
cask install dash 2> /dev/null
cask install transmit 2> /dev/null
cask install parallels 2> /dev/null
cask install tower 2> /dev/null
cask install codekit 2> /dev/null
